## 📂 Project Structure

```
SSD-Project/
├── src/
│   ├── dao/
│   │   ├── AuditLogDAO.java
│   │   ├── BookingDAO.java
│   │   ├── PaymentDAO.java
│   │   ├── RoomDAO.java
│   │   └── UserDAO.java
│   ├── model/
│   │   ├── Booking.java
│   │   ├── Payment.java
│   │   ├── Room.java
│   │   └── User.java
│   ├── service/            # Business logic & RBAC enforcement
│   ├── ui/                 # JavaFX FXML controllers per role
│   ├── util/               # DBConnection, BCryptUtil, AuditLogger
│   ├── config.properties   # DB credentials (gitignored)
│   └── Main.java           # Application entry point → loads LoginView.fxml
├── libs/                   # JavaFX SDK, jBCrypt, MySQL JDBC JAR
├── database.sql            # Full schema + seed data
└── .gitignore
|__ Screenshots             #Folder containing the screenshots of app working 
                             this folder is only for readme and can be deleted 
                             too its not part of project !
```
